{"tid":1687380,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【 #112 : Emergency Call for HK Autonomy 】#HongKongSOS","createTime":"2019-11-01T19:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T05:06:24.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b0852cefadedc5effd7e6f2d68219fed29540a3b","tid":1687380,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T19:12:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qFBX87B0NNU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqFBX87B0NNU&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8ITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=57a7ff20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qFBX87B0NNU</a><br />\n<br />\n【112: Emergency Call for HK Autonomy】<br />\n<br />\nOn 2 November (Sat), global rallies will be held in over 48 cities in 17countries in support of autonomy for Hong Kong, as promised in the Sino-British Joint Declaration and stated in our Basic Law. On &ldquo;112&rdquo; (also an emergency telephone number in parts of the world), we are calling on the world to take action to preserve Hong Kong&rsquo;s status as an international metropolis, and to make a principled stand against oppression backed by financial might.<br />\n#FightforAutonomy #StandWithHK #HongKongSOS #112<br />\n<br />\nStay tuned to latest updates on Facebook@StandwithHK<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/112HKSOS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F112HKSOS&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8ITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=d7b6cc46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/112HKSOS</a><br />\n<br />\n1. HONG KONG 👷 (112)<br />\nTime: 15:00<br />\nLocation: Victoria Park<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HK_112_SOS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHK_112_SOS&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8ITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=41532dba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HK_112_SOS</a><br />\n=============<br />\n2. London, UK 🇬🇧 (112)<br />\n3. Nottingham, UK 🇬🇧 (112)<br />\n4. Sheffield, UK 🇬🇧 (112)<br />\n5. Edinburgh, UK 🇬🇧 (112)<br />\n6. Exeter, UK 🇬🇧 (112)<br />\n7. Bath, UK 🇬🇧 (1 Nov)<br />\n8. Tokyo, JAPAN 🇯🇵 (112)<br />\n9. Calgary, CANADA 🇨🇦 (112)<br />\n10. Vancouver, CANADA 🇨🇦 (112)<br />\n11. Toronto, CANADA 🇨🇦 (112)<br />\n12. Winnipeg, CANADA 🇨🇦 (112)<br />\n13. Montreal, CANADA 🇨🇦 (3 Nov)<br />\n14. Victoria, CANADA 🇨🇦 (112)<br />\n15. Halifax, CANADA 🇨🇦 (112)<br />\n16. Edmonton, CANADA 🇨🇦 (112)<br />\n17. St. John&rsquo;s, CANADA 🇨🇦 (112)<br />\n18. Regina, CANADA 🇨🇦 (112)<br />\n19. Ottawa, CANADA 🇨🇦 (112)<br />\n20. Washington DC, USA 🇺🇸 (112)<br />\n21. Los Angeles, USA 🇺🇸 (112)<br />\n22. San Francisco, USA 🇺🇸 (112)<br />\n23. Boston, USA 🇺🇸 (112)<br />\n24. New York, USA 🇺🇸 (112)<br />\n25. San Diego, USA 🇺🇸 (112)<br />\n26. Seattle, USA 🇺🇸 (112)<br />\n27. Chicago, USA 🇺🇸 (1 Nov)<br />\n28. Sydney, AUSTRALIA 🇦🇺 (112)<br />\n29. Brisbane, AUSTRALIA 🇦🇺 (112)<br />\n30. Perth, AUSTRALIA 🇦🇺 (112)<br />\n31. Melbourne, AUSTRALIA 🇦🇺 (112)<br />\n32. Adelaide, AUSTRALIA 🇦🇺 (3 Nov)<br />\n33. Paris, FRANCE 🇫🇷 (112)<br />\n34. Frankfurt, GERMANY 🇩🇪 (112)<br />\n35. Hamburg, GERMANY 🇩🇪 (112)<br />\n36. Cologne, GERMANY 🇩🇪 (112)<br />\n37. Berlin, GERMANY 🇩🇪 (112)<br />\n38. Auckland, NEW ZEALAND 🇳🇿 (112)<br />\n39. Christchurch, NEW ZEALAND 🇳🇿 (112)<br />\n40. Taipei, TAIWAN 🇹🇼 (112)<br />\n41. Taichung, TAIWAN 🇹🇼 (112)<br />\n42. Brussels, BELGIUM 🇧🇪 (112)<br />\n43. Pretoria, SOUTH AFRICA 🇿🇦 (112)<br />\n44. Oslo, NORWAY 🇳🇴 (112)<br />\n45. Seoul, SOUTH KOREA 🇰🇷 (112)<br />\n46. Copenhagen, DENMARK 🇩🇰 (112)<br />\n47. Barcelona, SPAIN 🇪🇸 (112)<br />\n48. Rio de Janeiro, BRAZIL 🇧🇷 (112)<br />\nand counting...."},{"pid":"8154f4b83c0cfe004a07f9a9952e32ac7e7e8066","tid":1687380,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T19:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />